# â­ Summary in One Line Each

* **Hash Pointer:** Points to data and includes its fingerprint.
* **Hash Chain:** Links blocks using fingerprints so no block can be changed.
* **Merkle Tree:** Fast way to verify large data using a single top fingerprint.

